<h1>Friends</h1>

<p>Cool people whose websites you should also check out!</p>

<div class="not-prose mb-10">
  <ul>
    {% for friend in friends %}
    <li>
      <a class="group relative block px-2 py-1 mb-1 bg-slate-50/50 hover:bg-slate-100 focus:bg-slate-100 rounded-md" href="{{ friend.url }}" target="_blank">
        <span class="leading-none block font-semibold">{{ friend.name }}</span>
        <span class="leading-none opacity-75 block italic">{{ friend.clean_url }}</span>
        <svg class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 h-full pe-2 inline-block opacity-0 transition-all -translate-x-1 group-hover:translate-x-0 group-focus:translate-x-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus:opacity-100" width="1rem" height="1rem" version="2.0">
          <use href="#chevron-right" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</div>


<div class="outline-dashed outline-2 px-2 py-1 rounded-md leading-snug italic text-center mb-3">
  <b class="uppercase">Disclaimer:</b> This list is neither complete nor ordered in a specific way. Even if you might not be on this list now, I still cherish all of my friends! &hearts;
</div>